Muchidzidzo che[[taranyika]], '''chisipiti''' zvinoreva panzvimbo panobuda mvura ichitubuka yega ichibva pasi. Imwe mvura inonaya inosinina ichipinda pasi pevhu, apo inotevedza pane ivhu kana [[muzera]] wematombo ano[[bvinina]] (layer of permeable rock). Mvura iyi inokwezvewa kuenda kunzvimbo dziri pakaderera kuburikidza ne[[gunganidzo]] re '''Earth'''. Nokuda kwegunganidzo, mvura yemuvhu inoti kana yaungana pakaderera inodazve kuti igadzikane pasi ipapo kuita muchechetere unodanwa kunzi [[tafura yemvura]] - ''water table''.

Imwe nguva [[muzera]] wedombo rinobvinina unosvika paunobhudikira paunosangana nepane [[nhika]] pauso hwenyika.  Ipapa kana tafura yemvura iri pakakwirira kudarika nhika iyi, mvura inotubuka kubuda mudombo ichionekwa sechisipiti.

Mune dzimwe nzvimbo mvura iyoyi inokwanisa kunge yayerera ichibatana nemuzera wedombo rinopisa zvokuti inotubuka panyika yave kudziya kuita chisipiti chinopisa  - ''Hot springs''.
